  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">FIRE DISASTER VICTIMS RECOVERY CAMPAIGN</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will help complete an ongoing building apartment to shelter the homeless disabled couple (Uzor and wife)  and their five kids who were victims of a fire incident in a deprived rural community in Southeast Nigeria. The Fire Disaster Victims Recovery Campaign intends to complete a build RUWAI started for the family and provide food, clothing, healthcare support, water, and school items to recover from shocks. It will empower the couple with alternative income skills for livelihoods.</narrative>
  </description>
